            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            alt="Douro valley"
            src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x600/?douro-valley"
          />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Portugal (Douro Valley)</h3>
            <p>
              Wine harvests and river calm — perfect for romantic vineyard
              cruises.
            </p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Food &amp; Wine</span
              ><span class="tag">Romance</span><span class="tag">Luxury</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <a class="link" href="/destinations/douro-sep">Explore details</a>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8">
                Best for: Food &amp; Wine
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            alt="Hokkaido autumn"
            src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x600/?hokkaido"
          />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Japan (Hokkaido early autumn)</h3>
            <p>
              Early autumn colors and fresh seafood — a nature & food lover's
              delight.
            </p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Nature</span
              ><span class="tag">Food &amp; Wine</span
              ><span class="tag">Adventure</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <a class="link" href="/destinations/hokkaido-sep"
                >Explore details</a
              >
              <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8">
                Best for: Nature
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div
        style="
          text-align: center;
          margin-top: 18px;
          font-size: 13px;
          color: var(--muted);
        "
      >
        Tip: Click an experience tag to refine results. Use the traveller
        options to tailor recommendations.
      </div>
    </section>

    {% include "travellers/where-next/where-next-faq.njk" %} {% include
    "blocks/affiliate-disclaimer.njk" %}
    <footer>
      © <span id="year"></span> Paradize — Your gateway to curated travel
